Name: Bar Wisse
Review Text: It is worth a try. Very high quality in a cozy atmosphere. The Staff is very nice a friendly. They say you can find here the best chicken satay in town. It is true! Cakes are good too. Price/quality ratio is commensurate. Recommended for breakfast/lunch and dinner
